<dec f='include/SDL2/SDL_ttf.h' l='217' type='SDL_Surface * TTF_RenderText_Blended_Wrapped(TTF_Font * font, const char * text, SDL_Color fg, Uint32 wrapLength)'/>
<doc f='include/SDL2/SDL_ttf.h' l='211'>/* Create a 32-bit ARGB surface and render the given text at high quality,
   using alpha blending to dither the font with the given color.
   Text is wrapped to multiple lines on line endings and on word boundaries
   if it extends beyond wrapLength in pixels.
   This function returns the new surface, or NULL if there was an error.
*/</doc>
